From: C0mpanionii <c0mpanionii@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 4 Nov 2025 14:19:44 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Add ASRock GPU RGB controller support

- Add support for ASRock GPU RGB controllers (tested on RX 9070 XT Steel Legend)
- Implements I2C protocol reverse-engineered from SignalRGB
- Detects device at address 0x36 on AMD GPU I2C buses
- Supports 3 RGB zones: ARGB Header, Top Side, and Fan
- Uses pure I2C block read/write (not SMBus)
- Tested and working on ASRock RX 9070 XT Steel Legend 16GB (PCI ID 1002:7550, SubVendor 1849:5403)
