+/*---------------------------------------------------------*\
+| ASRockGPUSMBusController.h                                |
+|                                                           |
+|   Driver for ASRock GPU RGB controllers                   |
+|                                                           |
+|   Based on SignalRGB ASRock GPU.js plugin                 |
+|                                                           |
